    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! I have babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in pristine condition\u2014the paint is sparkling, the interior is spotless, and it runs like a total dream. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. It\u2019s truly the perfect find if you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag!",
      "price": 46500.0,
