    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep, original luster with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any wear or creasing, and all electronic systems function with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. Every component, from the smooth-shifting transmission to the factory-fresh undercarriage, reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a benchmark example of this model.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
