      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, maintained in what can only be described as showroom condition. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising level of care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Rigorously inspected to ensure peak mechanical performance and aesthetic perfection, this automobile represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer seeking an investment-grade acquisition.",
