      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It has been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered every single day. Honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot\u2014not a mark on it! If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the showroom price tag, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take a look, you're going to love it!",
