    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This naturally aspirated inline-six utilizes six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power through a factory limited-slip differential for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos overhaul to ensure long-term structural and mechanical integrity. The exterior retains its factory-original finish with zero imperfections, while the interior features pristine Nappa leather bolsters and functional, pixel-perfect instrumentation. This is a collector-tier example for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromised driving dynamics.",
